item.title:
Fans believe Paramore may be featured on ‘Speak Now (Taylor’s Version)’ due to Hayley Williams' response to a fan who gave her a bracelet of the album:
“This is coming at a very interesting time that you’re giving me this to wear, that's all I'll say.”

item.title:
Kanye West has been sued by a paparazzi for assault, battery and negligence after Kanye grabbed and threw her phone for photographing him back in January.
“He has no right to assault me, batter me or cause me to be afraid to pursue my profession.”
